Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================AVANT====================
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.80,0:00:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 请在回收同意书上签字
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.90,0:00:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不和米拉贝尔分别了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.31,0:00:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,以后会寂寞喽
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这孩子是棕熊小阿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.14,0:00:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,还有在米拉贝尔回收以后
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.20,0:00:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,作为所有者的你有三个选项
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.18,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,一个是重购时的优惠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.73,0:00:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,第二个是在换购时给您返现定价的30％
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.39,0:00:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,第三个是 给米拉贝尔的身体换上新的OS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是新的人格将她继续利用
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.05,0:00:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,请你们更换OS吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.54,0:00:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.22,0:00:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,人格和记忆不管怎么样都是会消失的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这样也没关系吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.78,0:00:51.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.81,0:00:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,因为以前我就这样做过
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.29,0:00:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,以前是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.14,0:00:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,就算更换了灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.93,0:01:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我也总把她当成是同一个人
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================TITLE====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.94,0:01:30.90,Title02,,0,153,165,,{\blur3\fad(500,500)}陌生的烟花
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================A-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.46,0:01:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.71,0:01:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.69,0:01:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我想更换了OS的Giftia
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.83,0:01:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会在某个特定机缘下找回原来的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.61,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不会的不会的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.21,0:01:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.58,0:01:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没有的事 没有前例
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.49,0:01:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.29,0:01:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,啥 你把这种问题问了一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,所以就说你是外行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.75,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你依然这么不近人情啊 美智瑠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.57,0:01:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Giftia的情况和人类丧失记忆是不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,因为它们是把整个内部系统换成新的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.71,0:02:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,完全是另一个东西了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.49,0:02:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这一点别搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,因此就可以认定这是没办法的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.26,0:02:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,无奈地怀着渺茫的希望才更痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.92,0:02:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好啦 你的心情我也理解
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.56,0:02:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,因为在来到这里之前 我也仔细想过同样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.09,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,美智瑠…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,所以说 一定要找到自己心中的妥协点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.90,0:02:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,都是毫无办法的事嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.73,0:02:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,小司 艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,明天第三终末服务课的狙击手被派遣到我们这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:47.34,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,982.5)}Terminal Service
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:47.34,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,982.5)}Marksman
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.80,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,第三？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.98,0:02:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那边负责的回收对象和所有者 似乎藏起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有消息说他们潜伏在我们的负责区域内呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以她要来我们这里找
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.66,0:03:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然事出突然很抱歉 但是我想让你们负责支援她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.44,0:03:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是 我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.51,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,小司
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们就是小司和艾拉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第三终末服务课的安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.99,0:03:17.24,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(990,982.5)}Terminal Service
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.61,0:03:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我们才是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.52,Default,,0,0,0,,话说 安迪的搭档呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.69,0:03:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,没来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,狙击手一个人出差不是常规吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:28.54,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(654,982.5)}Marksman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.94,0:03:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,第一课不一样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.59,0:03:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我没出过差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.73,0:03:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,专门派遣两个人 那样效率太低了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,因为出差地都会安排你们这样的专员来协助
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.36,0:03:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所以也不会有困难
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.97,0:03:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,但是如果艾拉要出差的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我绝对会跟去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我一个人也可以出差的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.03,0:03:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.34,0:04:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:04.97,Default,,0,0,0,,错误 我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.98,0:04:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:08.78,Back,,0,0,0,,我是为艾拉担心…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,你们真是一对奇特的组合呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.56,0:04:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 司司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.35,0:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你是…奥利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.57,0:04:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.09,0:04:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,真不敢相信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我的知心密友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.90,0:04:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.23,0:04:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你在摸哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.43,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然会反击 吓我一跳呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.54,0:04:42.77,Default,,0,0,0,,以前明明不论怎么玩弄 都会顺其自然的说
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样也别有一番风味…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.47,0:04:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.74,0:04:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,实话说 我们是一起度过青春时代的好闺蜜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.08,0:04:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你瞎说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.66,0:05:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我是第一次见你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你太像我的朋友了 让我搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我真是太冒失了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.76,0:05:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那 我失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,第一课的人都好有特点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.24,0:05:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,记忆消失了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.60,0:05:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.80,0:05:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.56,0:05:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们该放弃了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,请在这里签字
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.21,0:06:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.66,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,放过我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想和德雷克分开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.41,0:06:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那么至少让我们一起待到期限最后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不是还有一星期左右的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.42,0:06:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可能会再逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:41.02,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷克
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.50,0:06:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我说 安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,德雷克…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀 真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.72,0:07:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你们 让回收超乎预想地提早完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.73,0:07:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？怎么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.90,0:07:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,有必要那么强迫他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.56,0:07:20.26,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得那么做很容易同所有者产生纠纷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.77,0:07:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我早习惯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.44,0:07:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我们的工作正是粉碎回忆呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪没做错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,应该说在终末服务课里 那种做法才是常例
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:42.88,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(796.5,982.5)}Terminal Service
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.35,0:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,只有我们很特殊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.68,0:07:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,会主动关怀到所有者和回收对象的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.10,0:07:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,说起来这是佳月在三年前引入的做法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.38,0:08:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,拜她所赐 课长总是被总部批评说花太多经费了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.90,0:08:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你是在等我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.90,0:08:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我和安贵先生谈了些今天的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.60,0:08:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.24,0:08:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想跟小司谈天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那下次我会去找艾拉聊的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.85,0:08:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是分不出来呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.42,0:08:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那今天就到这
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拜啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.50,0:08:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才的是安迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.50,0:08:57.20,Default,,0,0,0,,想就之前的事向她道歉 所以给她打个电话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,结果她完全被我迷住了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有魅力的女人真是太辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 说起来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.54,0:09:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,听你口气 好像以前就认识安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我们以前是邻居
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那时她叫奥利维亚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,那时？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.76,0:09:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.58,0:09:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是安迪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.52,0:09:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,给人的感觉有点不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利维亚几年前被回收了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.61,0:09:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,那 难道说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,她更换了OS
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.96,0:09:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们终末服务课不是老被要求削减经费吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.66,0:09:46.48,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(687,982.5)}Terminal Serivice
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.87,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,所以呢 本应处理掉的奥利维亚 就被再利用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪有奥利维亚的记忆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.29,0:10:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真想不到会这样与她再会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,又揉到了那个软软的胸部啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,奥利维亚的胸部 虽然现在是安迪的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.42,0:10:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我以前总是揉到爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.61,0:10:14.08,Back,,0,0,0,,虽然正确来说都是我强迫她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.90,0:10:13.33,Default,,0,0,0,,这人没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠不在意她不再是奥利维亚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事不值得放在心里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真的是这样吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================B-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.88,0:10:48.50,Default,,0,0,0,,点心送来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.78,0:10:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 谁送的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,第三终末服务课的课长
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.61,0:10:53.12,Uptext,,0,0,0,,{\pos(930,982.5)}Terminal Service
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,真好呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉 上茶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.97,0:11:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,呀 之前来的安迪真是干练哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.75,0:11:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,来如影去如风的感觉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.48,0:11:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 你是说我们没用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.87,0:11:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,不不 我不是这个意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,司司
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.15,0:11:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,帮…帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.83,0:11:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我不小心跟安迪说了家乡的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.20,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她就死乞白赖地求我带她去看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.35,0:11:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.23,0:11:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,祭典就在今晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.49,0:11:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,所以司司 请你一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要我去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.48,0:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩好好玩不就好了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.66,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,办不到 办不到 办不到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.03,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.08,0:11:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,因为那里满是我与奥利维亚的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.98,0:11:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,要我和安迪两人去那里看祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.21,0:11:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,太折磨人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为她们的脸一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.52,0:12:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,所以司司 你要一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.76,0:12:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,就当是帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.76,0:12:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喘不过气来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.60,0:12:09.42,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,那俩人在说什么悄悄话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.52,0:12:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉 在听吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:19.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好在意呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.82,0:12:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我是在说 连搭档也瞒着是不是有什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不怎么在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.81,0:12:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,其实你超在意的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 只是说如果
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.77,0:12:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,带安迪去了祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,她会借此机会回想起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.15,0:12:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕一点点的奥利维亚的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的事可能吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在想艾艾的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.78,0:12:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.38,0:13:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,不管我怎么说 你也不会轻易接受的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.16,0:13:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,所以没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,司司就利用我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.77,0:13:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,利用是说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.44,0:13:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,在那里 用自己的眼睛确认就好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.85,0:13:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不用勉强的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我…我是小司的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.27,0:13:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便一说 安迪也一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.23,0:13:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠小姐也是肯定会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.97,0:13:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我…我去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.53,0:13:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 就这么定啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,听说最后还会放烟花 超级热闹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,至今为止我从没看过烟花
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.62,0:13:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.97,0:13:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,声音很响的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.64,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你肯定会吓一跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.20,0:13:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是不是要带耳塞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不用那么夸张啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.77,0:13:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就用手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.76,0:14:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 人真多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉 激萌激萌的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.79,0:14:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 不由得兴奋起来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我没什么机会来这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,和爱瑠交朋友真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.49,0:14:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们四处转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,小…小司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.65,0:14:37.41,Default,,0,0,0,,小司
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.58,0:14:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这张真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.77,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,全是我和爱瑠嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,也该给艾拉照几张呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.47,0:14:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.36,0:14:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,喝点什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好呀 有什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.24,0:14:57.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她们就像一对亲密的姐妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.94,0:15:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话 艾拉也来照几张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.40,0:15:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,错误 我听不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,请重说一次
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 照照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.17,0:15:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,错误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,错误
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.88,0:15:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你不高兴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.59,0:15:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你们俩 快来看这个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.52,0:15:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.70,0:15:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,是水母果汁呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.34,0:15:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,也算是这个祭典的特产了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想象不出味道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.66,0:15:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,什么呀 喝一口就知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.34,0:15:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 安迪还是别了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.26,0:15:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯～ 好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然第一次喝 但是味道不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是 这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,味道不错吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠不喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.76,0:15:48.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还…还好啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.45,0:15:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 那个是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.73,0:15:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,走吧走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.77,0:15:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,来呀 艾拉也去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.36,0:15:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小心别走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.95,0:16:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.81,0:16:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.43,0:16:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,才不会走散…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,小司 这个你也喝喝看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.68,0:16:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,欸 但是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.44,0:16:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.54,0:16:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,走散了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.18,0:16:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.49,0:16:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,大叔 再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪看起来好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.09,0:16:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,逛了好多地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.03,0:17:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得她的记忆回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊 这就是现实
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.25,0:17:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我明年不会来这个祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.00,0:17:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候我想和安迪一起去其他地方看看
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不想让安迪分享 我与奥利维亚在一起的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,而是想从现在开始创造新的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.09,0:17:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不这样做的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,对安迪和奥利维亚都会很失礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.00,0:17:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,爱瑠…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.12,0:17:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,今天谢谢你陪我们
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.77,0:17:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,多亏了你 我想我放开了心里的芥蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.34,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,一定要放手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.70,0:17:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 司司
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.50,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,能够创造回忆的只有现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,只有当下这个瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,当下这个瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.37,0:18:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,烟花…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.18,0:18:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 咦？ 艾拉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,难道是走散了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找她
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.88,0:18:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,好好干 小伙子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.35,0:19:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉 丢下你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.82,0:19:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你找到了我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,声音 很响的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 小司
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,安迪的记忆没有找回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,欸？为什么说这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说我让小司觉得痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.88,0:20:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是的话 我希望你说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.60,0:20:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我不想因做你的搭档 而让你痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.68,0:21:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我好痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.26,0:21:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛苦好痛苦 心痛得像被撕碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.16,0:21:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想永远做艾拉的搭档
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.98,0:21:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要做到这一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.00,0:21:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,还说为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.12,0:21:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.51,0:21:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢艾拉
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================C-PART====================
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我喜欢艾拉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.55,0:23:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 他说出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.14,0:23:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不…不…不…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.97,0:23:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.42,0:23:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================INJP====================
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.06,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}はぐれた君を探してたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.76,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}呼びかけた声かき消されて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.19,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}僕が握りしめたその手は
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.44,0:18:46.43,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}震えていたね
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.83,0:18:50.29,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}ふたりの想いが
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.63,0:18:55.46,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}戻せない時間抱きしめ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.91,0:19:00.31,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}高く飛んでくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.23,0:19:04.65,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}万華鏡空にきらめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.63,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}君がぎこちなく微笑んでて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.09,0:19:14.63,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}愛しさ溢れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.41,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}光が溶けてくその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.54,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}心から願うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.67,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}この瞬間を
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:31.96,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}永遠に忘れないようにと
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.67,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}数え切れない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:39.99,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}君との日々　振り向けばほら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.39,0:19:44.18,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}スターマインのよう
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.06,0:19:50.03,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}鮮やかに
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:11.12,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}朝焼けは虹色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.99,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}祭りの後ただひとり
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:20.80,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}君の余韻に浸る
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.81,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}ぬくもり抱いて歩き出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:29.50,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}この奇跡にありがとう
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:33.06,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}いつの日かまた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:37.91,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}巡り会えますように
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:42.50,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}万華鏡　空にきらめいて
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.58,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}君がぎこちなく微笑んでた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:52.63,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}愛しさ溢れてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:57.22,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}光が溶けてくその前に
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.52,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}心から誓ったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:04.44,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}この瞬間を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:11.84,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}永遠に忘れはしないと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:18.77,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}遠く　咲き乱れてる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:28.64,INJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}スターマイン空彩る
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================INCN====================
Dialogue: 1,0:18:31.67,0:18:35.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}寻找着你失却的身影
Dialogue: 1,0:18:35.39,0:18:38.76,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}声声呼唤不绝如缕
Dialogue: 1,0:18:39.08,0:18:42.19,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}紧紧握住的你的双手
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.44,0:18:46.43,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}这般颤抖不停
Dialogue: 1,0:18:46.83,0:18:50.29,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}我们的思念
Dialogue: 1,0:18:50.63,0:18:55.46,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}是无可回溯的时间
Dialogue: 1,0:18:55.91,0:19:00.31,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}让我们紧紧拥抱、跃向蓝天
Dialogue: 1,0:19:01.23,0:19:04.65,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}火树银花照亮今宵
Dialogue: 1,0:19:04.93,0:19:08.63,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}照亮你脸上笨笨的微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:19:09.09,0:19:14.63,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}架起我们心间的爱桥
Dialogue: 1,0:19:15.96,0:19:19.41,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}在光华消融而逝之前
Dialogue: 1,0:19:19.70,0:19:22.54,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}发自内心祈愿
Dialogue: 1,0:19:23.01,0:19:26.67,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}让这一瞬间
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.06,0:19:31.96,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}化作你我不忘的永远
Dialogue: 1,0:19:32.14,0:19:34.67,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}回首往昔
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.79,0:19:39.99,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}你我数不尽的回忆
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.39,0:19:44.18,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}瞧　就像那漫天焰火
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.06,0:19:50.03,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}花千树　星如雨
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.41,0:20:11.12,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}踏着祭典的尾声
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.62,0:20:14.99,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}七彩朝霞映出一影孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.39,0:20:20.80,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}沉浸于你的温软
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.36,0:20:25.81,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}携着你的歌声迈开步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.11,0:20:29.50,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}感谢这份奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.82,0:20:33.06,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}坚信我们有朝一日
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.52,0:20:37.91,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}必将再度萍水相逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.06,0:20:42.50,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}火树银花凋落在夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.76,0:20:46.58,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}你那笨笨的微笑也随之纷飞而去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.92,0:20:52.63,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}惟有你我心间的爱桥永恒不坠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.82,0:20:57.22,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}在光华消融而逝之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.55,0:21:00.52,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}发自内心祈愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:04.44,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}这一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.90,0:21:11.84,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}我永生不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:18.77,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}九霄之上　灿烂辉煌
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:28.64,INCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2.25}那是火树银花在夜空绽放
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,====================OPJP====================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.20,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}光をあつめて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:57.50,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}さよならの想い出を
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:04.86,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}瞳にたたえて　見つめる夢　遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:10.11,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}壊れてしまう　うたかたのメモリー
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:15.55,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}寂しさの涙　そっと拭こう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:22.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}伸ばした手は観覧車　優しくとらえて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:27.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}目覚めそうな　記憶の欠片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:33.90,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}うつむいて　消えてほしいと祈るけど
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:39.99,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}君が見つけてくれたこの声を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:47.04,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}動き出した時計の針　世界はやがて色付いて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:53.26,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}プラスティックな心が輝き出すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:58.12,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}忘れないで　おぼえていて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:23:05.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}いつかまた巡り逢える日まで
Comment: 0,0:21:41.04,0:21:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,====================OPCN====================
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.48,0:21:45.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}让光华汇聚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.10,0:21:57.50,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}一段段别离　浮现眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.76,0:22:04.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}梦里辗转　望断归来路
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.90,0:22:10.11,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}记忆如此飘渺
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:15.55,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}梦醒时分　独掩残泪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.90,0:22:22.71,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你的双手好似轮回的摩天轮　轻轻拂过我的心坎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:27.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}那些零落的记忆　仿佛在把我呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.19,0:22:33.90,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}只是我的愿景　却是流水落花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.13,0:22:39.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}你找到的这声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.41,0:22:47.04,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}让时钟开始回转　让世间染上色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:53.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}延异的心灵　便闪闪发光
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:53.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2\pos(750,1005)\fs30\fsp1.5}Plastic
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.50,0:22:58.12,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}请不要忘记　记住这一切
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.63,0:23:05.07,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be2}直到有朝一日　你我再度萍水相逢时
